{"lemma":"مُضْرِب","slug":"مُضْرِب","root":"ض.ر.ب","root_slug":"ض-ر-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ض-ر-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n25710","n25711","n25712","n25713","n25715"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8F%D8%B6%D9%92%D8%B1%D9%90%D8%A8"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"bat, racket (club used for striking the ball in sports)","examples":[{"text":"مَثَلاً، عِنْدَنَا فِي كَالِيفُورْنِيَا لَوْ كَانَ دُكَّان يَبِيع مَضَارِب التِّنِس، فَإِنَّ جَارَهُ لَنْ يَبِيع مَضَارِب التِّنِس أَيْضًا.","english":"For example, in California, if it were a shop selling tennis rackets, its neighbour would not sell tennis rackets either."}]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Morphologically from the root ض ر ب (ḍ r b)."},"ipa":["/midˤ.rab/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n25710","headword_ar":"مَضْرَبٌ","root":"Drb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"is an inf. n. (Ham p. 129.) [See the sentence explaining the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Daraba fiY AlA^aroDi","text_ar":"ضَرَبَ فِى الاَرْضِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and also the sentence next following it, towards the close of the first paragraph.] ―         -b2-  And it is also a noun of place [and of time, like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maDoribN","text_ar":"مَضْرِبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is the regular form]. (Ham ibid.) See the next paragraph, in five places."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n25711","headword_ar":"مَضْرِبٌ","root":"Drb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maDorabN","text_ar":"مَضْرَبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A place,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"time,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[the latter, as is said in the explanation of a phrase mentioned in what follows,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of beating, striking, smiting,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hitting:"},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b2-  and also, (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a place,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"time, of journeying."},{"kind":"text","text":"(KL.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maDoribu","text_ar":"مَضْرِبُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlZ~aribaAni","text_ar":"الظَّرِبَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The line,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"long mark, upon the face of the animal called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ZrbAn","text_ar":"ظربان"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as though it were a place upon which it had been struck]. (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zrb","text_ar":"ظرب"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maDoribN","text_ar":"مَضْرِبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A place where a tent is pitched,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"set up."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) ―         -b5-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miDorabN","text_ar":"مِضْرَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b6-  Also, (thus in the TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"swf","text_ar":"سوف"},{"kind":"text","text":", as from the A,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maDorabN","text_ar":"مَضْرَبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (thus in a copy of the A in the present art.,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"masaAfapN","text_ar":"مَسَافَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A space,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tract,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an extent, over which one journeys;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as being a place of beating the ground]: so in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baEiydN","text_ar":"بَعِيدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bayonahumo maDorabN","text_ar":"بَيْنَهُمْ مَضْرَبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maDoribN","text_ar":"مَضْرِبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e. (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Between them is a far-extending space to be traversed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) ―         -b7-  ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maDoribu EasalapK","text_ar":"مَضْرِبُ عَسَلَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a euphemism for (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The place of injection of sperma:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and hence it means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the source from which one springs; origin, ancestry,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"parentage;"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.] One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA A^aEorifu lahu maDoriba EasalapK","text_ar":"مَا اَعْرِفُ لَهُ مَضْرِبَ عَسَلَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A) meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEoraAqahu","text_ar":"اَعْرَاقَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e. (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I know not the sources"},{"kind":"text","text":"(or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the source"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from which he has sprung;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his ancestry,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"parentage"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA yuEorafu lahu maDoribu EasalapK","text_ar":"مَا يُعْرَفُ لَهُ مَضْرِبُ عَسَلَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"No source"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"origin"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"parentage"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"nor people, nor ancestor"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"father, nor nobility, pertaining to him, is know."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA lifulaAnK","text_ar":"مَا لِفُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maDoribu EasalapK","text_ar":"مَضْرِبُ عَسَلَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, in the latter"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lizayodK","text_ar":"لِزَيْدٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":",) i. e. (tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one has no source"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of kindred"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nasab","text_ar":"نَسَب"},{"kind":"text","text":"),"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"nor of cattle"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"property"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maAl","text_ar":"مَال"},{"kind":"text","text":"). (S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~ahu lakariymu","text_ar":"اـِنَّهُ لَكَرِيمُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmaDoribi","text_ar":"المَضْرِبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily he is generous in respect of origin"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A, TA.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DariybapN","text_ar":"ضَرِيبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b8-  One says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^atati Aln~aAqapu EalaY maDoribihaA","text_ar":"اَتَتِ النَّاقَةُ عَلَى مَضْرِبِهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The she-camel arrived at the time"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of year"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of her being leaped by the stallion;"},{"kind":"text","text":"making the time to be like the place. (S.) ―         -b9-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maDoribN","text_ar":"مَضْرِبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, O, and so in the M in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rm","text_ar":"رم"},{"kind":"text","text":",) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maDorabN","text_ar":"مَضْرَبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, * TA,) with fet-h to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"m","text_ar":"م"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) and to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"r","text_ar":"ر"},{"kind":"text","text":"also, (TA,) [but this is app. a mistake, as the weight of authority is in favour of the former,] (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A bone in which is marrow:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a bone that is broken and from which marrow is extracted"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sought to be extracted"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (M in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rm","text_ar":"رم"},{"kind":"text","text":".) One says, of a sheep or goat, (S, A,) that is emaciated, (S,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA yurim~u minohaA maDoribN","text_ar":"مَا يُرِمُّ مِنْهَا مَضْرِبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Not a bone of her that is broken for its marrow contains any marrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; i. e. when a bone of her is broken, no marrow"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1783},{"kind":"text","text":"will be found in it. (S, A.) ―         -b10-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maDoribN","text_ar":"مَضْرِبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maDorabN","text_ar":"مَضْرَبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maDoribapN","text_ar":"مَضْرِبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maDorabapN","text_ar":"مَضْرَبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maDorubapN","text_ar":"مَضْرُبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sb, TA) signify The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"part"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a sword,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with which one strikes:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, and Ham p. 129:) or [the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"part"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"about a span from the extremity:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"part exclusive of,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"below, the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Zubap","text_ar":"ظُبَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.] ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"duwna AlT~ubapi","text_ar":"دُونَ الطُّبَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"): (TA:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"edge"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Had~","text_ar":"حَدّ"},{"kind":"text","text":") thereof; (K, TA;) thus expl. by several of the leading lexicologists: (TA:) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DariybapN","text_ar":"ضَرِيبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": which last also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a sword:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) [i. e.] a sword itself is sometimes thus called, as ISd says: (TA:) the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maDoribN","text_ar":"مَضْرِبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maDaAribu","text_ar":"مَضَارِبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Ham ubi suprà.) ―         -b11-  ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maDoribu mavalK","text_ar":"مَضْرِبُ مَثَلٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The secondary idea,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thing, signified by a parable"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"proverb, and compared to the primary idea,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thing; the thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"case, to which a parable"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"proverb is applied:"},{"kind":"text","text":"correlative of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maworidu mavalK","text_ar":"مَوْرِدُ مَثَلٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":": pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maDaAribu","text_ar":"مَضَارِبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b12-  And [the pl.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maDaAribu","text_ar":"مَضَارِبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Stratagems in war."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","A","K","TA","O","Msb","Sb"]},{"entry_id":"n25712","headword_ar":"مُضْرِبٌ","root":"Drb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[part. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aDoraba","text_ar":"اَضْرَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.]. You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raA^ayotu Hay~apF muDoribFA","text_ar":"رَاَيْتُ حَيَّةً مُضْرِبًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muDoribapF","text_ar":"مُضْرِبَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I saw a serpent still, not moving."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n25713","headword_ar":"مِضْرَبٌ","root":"Drb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thing with which one beats, strikes, smites,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hits;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing with which the action termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlD~arob","text_ar":"الضَّرْب"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is performed;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miDoraAbN","text_ar":"مِضْرَابٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A wooden instrument"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a kind of mallet"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with which the bow-string is struck in the operation of separating cotton."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) ―         -b2-  And, (S, A, K,) as an epithet applied to a man, (S, A,) it signifies"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$adiydu","text_ar":"شَدِيدُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlD~arobi","text_ar":"الضَّرْبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[One"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who beats, strikes, smites,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hits, vehemently"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (S, O;) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaviyru AlD~arobi","text_ar":"كَثِيرُ الضَّرْبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[one"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who beats,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"much"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaruwbN","text_ar":"ضَرُوبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Dar~aAbN","text_ar":"ضَرَّابٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DariybN","text_ar":"ضَرِيبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaribN","text_ar":"ضَرِبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O, K, TA. [But in none of these lexicons is this signification mentioned in such a manner as to show that it necessarily relates to any but the first of these words, namely,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miDorabN","text_ar":"مِضْرَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": that it does so, however, is indicated by the measures of all of them.]) ―         -b3-  Also, (O, K, TA,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maDoribN","text_ar":"مَضْرِبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", with fet-h to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"m","text_ar":"م"},{"kind":"text","text":"and kesr to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"r","text_ar":"ر"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh,) [thus] written like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majolisN","text_ar":"مَجْلِسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"by MF, and pronounced by the vulgar"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maDorab","text_ar":"مَضْرَب"},{"kind":"text","text":", but both of these are [said to be] incorrect, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tent such as is called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qub~ap","text_ar":"قُبَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Mgh:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a great"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tent of the kind called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fusoTaAT","text_ar":"فُسْطَاط"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (O, K, TA;) the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fsTAT","text_ar":"فسطاط"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a king:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maDaAribu","text_ar":"مَضَارِبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Mgh, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","A","K","TA","O","Mgh"]},{"entry_id":"n25715","headword_ar":"مُضَرَّبٌ","root":"Drb","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Sewed"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quilted"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with cotton:"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied in this sense to a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bisaAT","text_ar":"بِسَاط"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or thing that is spread like a carpet, &c.]. (Mgh, Msb.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]}}